'''2008年喬戈里峰事故'''是2008年一次發生於[[喬戈里峰|喬戈里峰]]的事故。17名登山者在登頂過程中遭遇[[雪崩|雪崩]]，造成11名登山者死亡，是史上攀登喬戈里峰犧牲人數最多的一次事故<ref name=bbc_2008_0803>{{cite news
 |url         = http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/south_asia/7539543.stm
 |title       = Eleven climbers feared dead on K2
 |publisher   = BBC News
 |date        = 2008-08-03
 |accessdate  = 2008-08-06
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20080804001657/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/south_asia/7539543.stm
 |archivedate = 2008-08-04
 |deadurl     = yes
}}</ref><ref>The most deadly climbing ''season'' on K2 was in 1986, when thirteen climbers died in seven separate accidents. See Curran pp. 183–207</ref>。

